FBIS4-31598 "dreeu113_p_94003" FBIS-EEU-94-113 Daily Report 10 Jun 1994 POLAND Sejm Adopts Amendment Easing Antiabortion Law Sejm Adopts Amendment Easing Antiabortion Law LD1006200694 Warsaw PAP in Polish 1942 GMT 10 Jun 94 LD1006200694 Warsaw PAP Polish BFN [Text] Warsaw, 10 Jun--The Sejm adopted an amendment to the Penal Code today that permits abortion in the event of the woman's "difficult living conditions or complicated personal situation." The act was adopted as proposed by the Parliamentary Women's Group and supported by more than 200 deputies. Two hundred and forty-one deputies voted for the act, 107 were against, and 32 abstained.
